  "text": "In this paper, based on the framework of [CITATION_1] , we continue to study the relations between these irreducible strata of AS g with the aim of finding sufficient conditions for the moduli space to be connected. Corollary 1.2 of [CITATION_2] implies that AS g is irreducible and thus connected when p = 2. For p > 2, the same corollary only tells us that AS g is connected for small values of g. We are able to prove that for p = 3, the moduli space AS g is also connected for all g. When p > 3, the following result, which implies that AS g is connected for g sufficiently large, is the main result of this paper. Theorem 1.1. When p = 3, the moduli space AS g is connected for any g.",
